ENCAPSULATION:
(i) Setter + Getter
1. Make Variables private
2. Set their values using setter method
3. get the assigned values through getter method
4. Apply logic on retrieved values bt creating methods which uses getter method values

(i) Constructor + Getter
1. Make Variables private
2. Set their values using constructors
3. get the assigned values through getter method
4. Apply logic on retrieved values bt creating methods which uses getter method values

(i) Constructor + Setter+ Getter
1. Make Variables private
2. Set their values using constructors and if needed update the value using Setter method
3. get the assigned values through getter method
4. Apply logic on retrieved values bt creating methods which uses getter method values

(i) Private methods encapsulated inside public method...
    => not to show irrelevant information to the user